# Per-device topic ACL (used in production with allow_anonymous false + password_file).
# Each device authenticates as username == its device id; %u expands to it.
# Devices are confined to their own namespace — NO wildcard subscribe (prevents
# one board from reading another child's data). See docs/README.md §6.5.

pattern readwrite edu/site1/%u/#
pattern read      edu/site1/group/+/cmd/#

# Backend / dashboard service account — broad read + command publish only.
user backend
topic read  edu/#
topic write edu/site1/+/cmd/#
topic write edu/site1/group/+/cmd/#
